{"type": "article", "id": 15453, "title": "江湖丛谈", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 6617, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606051922105JDVKoCi6cgMdxwA.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.7359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.cn/%E6%B1%9F%E6%B9%96%E4%B8%9B%E8%B0%88-%E8%BF%9E%E9%98%94%E5%A6%82/dp/B006YI11S2/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1443100768&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=%E6%B1%9F%E6%B9%96%E4%B8%9B%E8%B0%88\" target=\"_blank\">《江湖丛谈》</a>，连阔如</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\">这是我国仅存的一部全面介绍江湖行当、行话和内幕的书籍。刘同说，“今年移动互联网经济，大家都在玩创业、做创新，从众筹到大数据各种新名词翻新不断，仔细拨开云雾，看《江湖丛谈》，发现最终故事也和天桥上的把戏差不多。甚至套话、谎话、夸张的话都一模一样。”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}